column2: SELECT m.specz_id, m.specz_ra, m.specz_dec, (m.specz_redshift - f.z) /m.specz_redshift AS z_distance, n.objid, n.distance, f.z, f.zErr, f.specobjid, f.petroMag_g - f.petroMag_i AS gminusi, gsl.h_alpha_eqw, gsl.h_alpha_eqw_err, gsl.h_alpha_flux, gsl.h_alpha_flux_err, gsl.h_alpha_cont_err, gsl.h_alpha_flux / gsl.h_alpha_cont AS h_alpha_blended_eqw, gsl.h_beta_eqw, gsl.h_beta_eqw_err, gsl.h_beta_flux, gsl.h_beta_flux_err, gsl.h_beta_cont_err, gsl.h_beta_flux / gsl.h_beta_cont AS h_beta_blended_eqw into mydb.s1#a_lines from MyDB.sdssmatches_s1#a AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.specz_ra, m.specz_dec, #) AS n JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS f ON n.objid = f.objid JOIN GalSpecLine as gsl on f.SpecObjID = gsl.SpecObjID
